name: Yorbeau Resources Inc. Class A Common Shares
longDescription: Yorbeau Resources Inc is involved in the exploration of mineral properties in the Province of Quebec. The company's project includes Rouyn Ellison, Beschefer, Scott Lake and many more. The operating segment of the company is Mining Exploration.
